  "texts": [
    "In the medical field, obtaining large amounts of data from a single institution can be challenging due to privacy and security concerns.",
    "Domain adaptation techniques can be used to transfer knowledge from pre-trained models to a new dataset with a different distribution.",
    "This can be particularly useful for tasks like disease diagnosis, where the model needs to be trained on data from multiple institutions to ensure generalizability.",
    "As mentioned earlier, multimodal data integration is an essential area of research in medical informatics.",
    "Transfer learning can be used to leverage pre-trained models from different modalities to improve the overall system's performance."
  ],
